<section class="mission" data-reveal>
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="tag">// why rustok</div>
    <blockquote class="quote">
      Rustok gives an AI agent a wallet of <span class="accent">its own</span> — self-custody, no
      middleman — so agents can take part in the economy directly: paying for the compute, data,
      and tools they rely on.
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission {
    padding: clamp(56px, 7vw, 100px) clamp(20px, 4vw, 56px);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-3) 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
  }
  .inner { max-width: 820px; }
  .tag { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted-2); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .quote {
    margin: 0; font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3.4vw, 38px); line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--text); text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .accent { color: var(--teal); }
</style>
